<div class="container-fluid row" style="margin-top:-1.5cm;margin-left:-1.2cm;margin-right:-1.2cm;">

  <div  class="col-lg-12" >

        <div class="homescreen" style="background-image: url(<%= asset_path 'hands6.jpg' %>);" >
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-1">
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-5" >
          <div style="background-color :#ffffff">
            <p style="text-align:center ; margin-top:2cm">
                
                <div class="well well-lg"><h3>Donation platform</h3><br>

                  Donation Platform web application creates a positive community of donors. The platform also helps Non-Governmental Organizations (NGOs) and Charities build awareness, credibility, and flexibility.
                  <br><br>Constant updates and follow ups will be provided by NGOs for donors to witness the impact of their donations
   The platform offers an easy and structured method to communicate with donors and facilitate donations.
                </div>
                
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>


        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <div  class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-6">

              <%= link_to donor_register_path do %>
              <p class="btn btn-default btn-lg" style="font-size:160%;
              width:75%;border-radius: 15px; margin-top:9cm ">
              Sign up</p>
                <%end%>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-6">
              <%= link_to organizations_path do %>
              <p class="btn btn-default btn-lg" style="font-size:160%;
              width:75%;border-radius: 15px; margin-top:9cm ">
            Organizations</p>
                <%end%>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
